{"tid":1248372,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲試過「積欠」（爭）垃圾和記錢","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:20:39.000Z","uid":190187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4623130586b97f8a12a29c806f2efc5a83b0d2","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"話說之前用和記，廢過屎，嬲嬲地轉咗台cut撚咗佢。<br />\n<br />\n點知搞好曬轉台手續，停用咗之後，和記夠膽死叫我交多一個月錢，但係嗰個月已經一早通知咗和記，而且佢都已經cut咗個網路無得用。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢搵咗間「商業信用情報有限公司」寄信嚇鳩我叫我快啲交錢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係<strong>採取進一步行動</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗，唔交會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52305e8e67d15c1e63c472c3be74cbc9e243bd09","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae0a026c99b8cbfc6cade1dccc18e4289e03f76","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"到底會唔會有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span></span>"},{"pid":"5dfa6e0eb974a9b47baf774acde86f4e1d0b3d09","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登無巴絲試過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d2517b7f8f316292a51162dd777d12dbbce435f4","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9996537177c0f4d8ef9dbc8b4c8877c16da23ff8","tid":1248372,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply